    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234380/extras/349ec87800f7d6abc800a15dc96b2286.poster.avif?t=1768132971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234380/extras/349ec87800f7d6abc800a15dc96b2286.webm?t=1768132971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234380/extras/349ec87800f7d6abc800a15dc96b2286.mp4?t=1768132971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《人偶看护者》——这是一款心理恐怖游戏，您将扮演一名在诡异恐怖宅邸中照料人偶的保姆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索环境、照看人偶，并找出其中的冒牌货。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎎 照顾人偶日常<br>🍽️ 喂食照料<br>🛁 沐浴更衣<br>🧵 检查修复<br>📖 讲睡前故事助眠</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234380/extras/45e11c1fc5a7867abd5c39dfd97e7f91.poster.avif?t=1768132971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234380/extras/45e11c1fc5a7867abd5c39dfd97e7f91.webm?t=1768132971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234380/extras/45e11c1fc5a7867abd5c39dfd97e7f91.mp4?t=1768132971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕵️ 找出冒牌者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔍 探索环境收集线索</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👁 检查人偶异常</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗣 询问其他人偶</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔦 使用紫外线灯/收音机/相机发现隐藏证据</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234380/extras/662986abf8b177f618fe587f36c7fe3e.poster.avif?t=1768132971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234380/extras/662986abf8b177f618fe587f36c7fe3e.webm?t=1768132971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗝️ 收集足够证据后，将冒牌人偶锁入箱子——但请记住，一旦选错，你将付出生命的代价。</p>",
